          "By now you've met hundreds of Norman",
          "words one at a time. Tier 4 shows you",
          "the shapes they share — the fingerprints",
          "that give them away.",
          "",
          "Endings: -tion, -age, -ment, -ance",
          "motion, village, judgment, distance",
          "",
          "Sound shifts the Normans brought with",
          "them from northern France:",
          "",
          "  gu → w    guard / ward",
          "  ca → ch   catch / chase",
          "  ca → ch   cattle / chattel",
          "",
          "Once you see these shapes, you'll",
          "spot Norman words on every page you",
          "read for the rest of your life."
